section_title: Compilation and synthesis of fifth national communications
sentences: This agenda sub-item (FCCC/SBI/2011/INF.1, FCCC/SBI/2011/INF.1/Add.1-2) was first addressed in the SBI plenary on 10 June.
It was further considered in a contact group co-chaired by Helen Plume and Diann Black Layne.
During the closing plenary on 16 June, the SBI agreed to continue consideration of the issue at SBI 35.
